costs more to trade. The</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1648469312/image_1648469312.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742120-ewg-facing-growth-challenges-and-may-exhibit-higher-volatility", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 22:20:43"}, {"id": "4742132", "title": "Thoughtful Investments Are The Only Ones Worth Making", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Conceptual image of man using smartphone to view bar graph\" data-id=\"1359134494\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1138px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">We Are</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Canadian government\u2019s plan to constrain population growth by reducing immigration over the next few years is designed to relieve demand pressure on key services like housing, education and health care. That\u2019s needed.</p> <p>The downsides are that</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742132-thoughtful-investments-only-ones-worth-making", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 22:10:00"}, {"id": "4742115", "title": "Ideaya Biosciences: Long-Tailed Pipeline With Positive Mid-Stage Data And Huge Cash", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business on Wall Street in Manhattan\" data-id=\"1220627489\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6240px\" height=\"4160px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Pgiam/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4656120-ideaya-biosciences-stock-an-opportunity-missed-rating-downgrade\">covered</a> <b>Ideaya Biosciences, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IDYA\" title=\"IDEAYA Biosciences, Inc.\">IDYA</a></span>) in December last year, and the stock had a great run for a while, before returning more or less to its December position. That \"idiopathic\" bullish run started in early January and continued</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742115-ideaya-biosciences-long-tailed-pipeline-with-positive-midstage-data-and-huge-cash", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 22:00:56"}, {"id": "4742126", "title": "Super Micro's Turning Point", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"3d rendering of crypto mining computer center\" data-id=\"1384239426\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384239426/image_1384239426.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty